title: Nearby notes can be used the same way.
pid: 521988e2-1d5f-4e63-ada2-4c84eea56304
body: |2-
  Consider moving up from the 12 to the 24-tone system:
  In 12 tones, you know riffs that use the notes {0,1,3},
  and also riffs that used {0,2,3}. Replacing the 1 or the 2
  from any of those riffs with the 1.5 that 24-edo makes available
  will probably sound good too.
